F2555OYjimc wrote a review Dec 2018
Hong Kong, China34 contributions45 helpful votes
Da Nang Hotel
The Hotel rooms are very spacious and clean. The furniture is modern and the bed was very comfortable and well kept. The bathroom was large with a larger shower area with multiple shower heads, hand held and overhead. Bed room has a kitchenette with cooktop, microwave, coffee maker. The hotel has a very nice breakfast buffet on the second floor with made to order eggs and omeletes.
Response from ALC S, Người quản lý at A La Carte Da Nang Beach
